8. **Text Formatting**: Extracting the text itself might require ignoring or properly interpreting text formatting commands (like `\textbf`, `\emph`, etc.) to get the plain content.

9. **Encoding and Special Characters**: Special characters in LaTeX (like `&`, `%`, `{`, `}`, etc.) require proper handling to ensure they're parsed as part of the content and not as control sequences.
